-logo-lg-1.png\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"AIOSEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"https://aioseo.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"width\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"32\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"height\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"32\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:4:\"item\";a:10:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:120:\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=what-is-the-seo-preview-tool\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 14:03:27 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"search snippets\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"seo inspector\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"seo preview tool\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"SERP optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"social snippets\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=142412\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:443:\"<p>Wondering what the SEO Preview tool is and how it can help you drive more traffic to your site? Your first interaction with users on search engine results pages (SERPs) is through your search snippets. And the SEO Preview tool&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\">What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12577:\"<p>Wondering what the SEO Preview tool is and how it can help you drive more traffic to your site?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your first interaction with users on search engine results pages (SERPs) is through your search snippets. And the SEO Preview tool helps ensure your search listings get more clicks than competitors’ search listings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll explain the SEO Preview tool and how it can help you drive more traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-1 wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-the-seo-preview-tool\">What is the SEO Preview Tool?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-use-the-seo-preview-tool\">How To Use the SEO Preview Tool</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-open-the-seo-preview-tool\">Step 2: Open the SEO Preview Tool</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-check-and-optimize-your-search-and-social-snippets\">Step 3: Check and Optimize Your Search and Social Snippets</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-use-the-seo-inspector-to-check-basic-seo-and-meta-tags\">Step 4: Use the SEO Inspector to Check Basic SEO and Meta Tags</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-the-seo-preview-tool-helps-you-drive-more-traffic-to-your-site\">How the SEO Preview Tool Helps You Drive More Traffic to Your Site</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-boost-organic-clickthrough-rates-ctr\">Boost Organic Clickthrough Rates (CTR)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-drive-engagement\">Drive Engagement</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-improve-rankings\">Improve Rankings</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-seo-preview-tool-a-game-changer-to-help-increase-rankings\">The SEO Preview Tool: A Game Changer to Help Increase Rankings</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-the-seo-preview-tool\">What is the SEO Preview Tool?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The SEO Preview tool in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"All In One SEO\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO) is a powerful feature that lets you get a glimpse of your search and social snippets right from within WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The tool shows you how your search snippets will appear on SERPs and how your Facebook and Twitter snippets will look when your content is shared on social media.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is important for many reasons, mainly because it helps you optimize your snippets to drive traffic. It also results in a boost in SEO. But more on that in a moment.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-the-seo-preview-tool\">How To Use the SEO Preview Tool</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the SEO Preview tool is super easy. Here’s how to get the most out of this revolutionary feature:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step to using the SEO Preview tool is to install and activate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best SEO plugins on the market and it comes with the SEO Preview tool.\" class=\"wp-image-100113\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the world’s best WordPress SEO plugin, boasting over 100 million downloads. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust AIOSEO to help them dominate SERPs and drive relevant traffic to their sites. This is because the plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one of the most beloved features in AIOSEO is the brand-new SEO Preview module.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful module makes it easy to optimize your search snippets, so they drive more traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-2-open-the-seo-preview-tool\">Step 2: Open the SEO Preview Tool</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve installed and activated AIOSEO, log in to your WordPress dashboard and go to your <strong>AIOSEO menu. </strong>Next,<strong> </strong>click on <strong>SEO Preview</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"702\" height=\"308\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-frontend.png\" alt=\"You can access the SEO Preview tool from your WordPress admin dashboard.\" class=\"wp-image-143343\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-frontend.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-frontend-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-frontend-600x263.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This will open the SEO Preview tool, where you can check and optimize your Google search and social snippets and inspect other SEO data.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-3-check-and-optimize-your-search-and-social-snippets\">Step 3: Check and Optimize Your Search and Social Snippets</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once in the SEO Preview tool, you can see how your search and social snippets will appear. Check them to see if they’re properly optimized.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"702\" height=\"601\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-google-1.png\" alt=\"The SEO Preview tool shows you what your search and social snippets will look like.\" class=\"wp-image-140576\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-google-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-google-1-300x257.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-google-1-600x514.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After inspecting your snippets, editing them is as easy as clicking the <strong>Edit Snippet</strong> button. Doing so will take you back to AIOSEO’s meta box for search snippets and the Social settings tab for social media snippets. This will enable you to edit and optimize your snippets.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-step-4-use-the-seo-inspector-to-check-basic-seo-and-meta-tags\">Step 4: Use the SEO Inspector to Check Basic SEO and Meta Tags</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides optimizing your search and social snippets, the SEO Preview tool lets you get an overview of your basic SEO and meta tags.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"550\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-seo-inspector.png\" alt=\"The SEO Inspector gives you an overview of your basic SEO and the meta tags on your page.\" class=\"wp-image-140578\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-seo-inspector.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-seo-inspector-300x236.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/seo-preview-frontend-seo-inspector-600x471.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Any errors revealed by the SEO Inspector can easily be corrected by clicking the <strong>Edit Post</strong> button. This will open your post or page in editor mode so you can work on your meta tags and other basic SEO issues.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-the-seo-preview-tool-helps-you-drive-more-traffic-to-your-site\">How the SEO Preview Tool Helps You Drive More Traffic to Your Site</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Search and social snippets play a huge role in boosting your SEO. This is why the SEO Preview tool is a critical feature that can help drive more traffic to your site. Here’s how:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-boost-organic-clickthrough-rates-ctr\">Boost Organic Clickthrough Rates (CTR)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Organic clickthrough rate refers to the percentage of users who see your search listing on SERPs and click on it. To increase your CTR, your search snippets must be optimized to prove search intent. A few ways to do this are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Include your keyword in the title, meta description, and URL</li><li>Craft your meta description as a mini sales pitch</li><li>Ensure your snippet matches search intent</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Doing this will help you create snippets that are helpful to users, resulting in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">increased CTRs</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-drive-engagement\">Drive Engagement</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Well-optimized search and social snippets are essential to driving engagement with your posts. Design them to elicit users&#8217; reactions so they click on the link, read your article, and even leave comments.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To further improve your engagement rates on social media, AIOSEO allows you to choose the image to be displayed in the social snippets. When you click the <strong>Edit Facebook Meta Data</strong> button (or <strong>Edit Twitter Meta Data</strong> button), you’ll be taken to the <strong>Social</strong> settings page, where you can choose the image source for the social snippet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"702\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-tool-social-1-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO also gives you the option to choose the image to be displayed in the social snippets.\" class=\"wp-image-143346\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-tool-social-1-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-tool-social-1-1-300x168.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seo-preview-tool-social-1-1-600x335.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to use an image that’s relevant to your content. Your images should also be attractive and engaging.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-improve-rankings\">Improve Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Optimized search snippets play a huge role in helping boost your SEO. One reason is that they help search engines better understand your content, resulting in better indexing. As a result, your content will show up for the keywords you’re targeting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason you’ll enjoy a boost in SEO is that the increased CTRs and higher engagement signal to search engines that users find your content helpful. This leads to your content being ranked higher.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember, for this to happen, you must take time to create optimized snippets.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-seo-preview-tool-a-game-changer-to-help-increase-rankings\">The SEO Preview Tool: A Game Changer to Help Increase Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Search and social snippets are powerful elements of your SEO strategy. Ensuring they are optimized results in more traffic and a boost in SEO. That’s why you must leverage the SEO Preview tool in AIOSEO to ensure your snippets are engaging, attractive, and follow <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\">SEO best practices</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you know what the SEO Preview tool is and how you can use it to drive traffic to your site. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> and our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/the-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-multilingual-seo/\">beginner’s guide to multilingual SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\">What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_